attributes.Long form description: The student begins by unscrewing the hex socket heads from the first leg and then the hex socket heads from the second leg and place the hex socket heads on the table. Then the student unscrews the top hex socket heads from the third leg and then the bottom hex socket heads from the first leg, the student unscrews the top hex socket head from the fourth leg and then removes the rest of the hex socket heads from the third leg. When the student finish removing the top table from the furniture, he then removes the last hex socket heads from the fourth leg and then the student disassembles the shelf from the furniture and disassembles the legs off. Finally he places all on the table.
